Package: UNKstats
Title: A Package for Teaching UNK Biostats
Version: 0.1.0.0
Authors@R:
    c(
      person(given = "Caleb", family = "Rother",
             email = "rotherc@lopers.unk.edu",
             role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides student-friendly wrappers around common statistical
    tests (ANOVA, repeated measures, Kruskal-Wallis, factorial ANOVA, etc.) 
    with ggplot visualizations and compact letter displays for post-hoc tests.
